  "title": "Buttery Velvety Avocado Mousse",
  "description": "This dairy-free indulgent Italian dish is rich and creamy with a perfect blend of buttery texture and velvety smoothness. Seasoned with sea salt, it's an easy-to-make dessert that pairs well with fresh fruits or as a standalone treat.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
